lead_paragraph: Jon Lester pitched seven strong innings in his season debut and the Chicago Cubs got home runs from Anthony Rizzo, Dexter Fowler and Matt Szczur in a 6-1 victory over the Los Angeles Angels on Tuesday night.

headline.print_headline: Cubs Hit 3 Homers for Lester in 6-1 Win Over Angels
